title: Donald Trump Implies George W. Bush Is To Blame For 9/11 — Jeb Bush Fires Back
text: The always outspoken and straight-shooting presidential candidate Donald Trump suggested that former president of the United States, George W. Bush is to blame for the 9/11 terrorist attacks, according to the New York Post. Trump was speaking about national emergencies, such as the 9/11 attacks of 14 years ago when he began discussing his qualifications...
